---
title: Grilled BBQ Striploin Steak and Sweet Pepper Wraps with Corn and Baby Veggie Salad
description: Juicy striploin and sweet peppers are lovingly wrapped in a cheesy toasted flatbread, and that's just one of three components in this grill recipe. Paired with sweet corn and a side salad of juicy tomatoes with crisp cucumbers, dinner tonight is a celebration of summer BBQ flavours.

Ingredients: Striploin steak • Flatbread (enriched wheat flour, water, canola oil, yogurt (milk ingredients, modified corn starch, carrageenan, pectin, active bacterial culture), milk, yeast, buttermilk, sugar, vinegar, salt, wheat gluten, corn flour, guar gum, vegetable monoglycerides, baking powder, soy lecithin, natural flavours, calcium propionate, potassium sorbate, calcium propionate, sodium bicarbonate, sorbic acid, enzymes) (milk, soy, wheat) • Corn • Sweet bell pepper • Cucumber • Baby tomatoes • Monterey Jack cheese (pasteurized milk, modified milk ingredients, cream, salt, microbial enzymes, bacterial culture, calcium chloride, cellulose, natamycin) (milk) • BBQ sauce (sugars (sugar/glucose-fructose, blackstrap molasses, brown sugar), tomato paste, vinegar, water, salt, modified corn starch, mustard, modified tapioca starch, mustard bran, chili peppers, soybean oil, garlic powder, onion powder, hydrolyzed corn protein, spices, seasoning, natural flavour, xanthan gum, caramel, citric acid, malic acid, sodium benzoate) (mustard) • Mayonnaise (canola and/or soy oil, liquid whole egg, frozen egg yolk, water, salt, sugar, vinegar, concentrated lemon juice, spice extract, mustard, lactic acid, calcium disodium EDTA) (mustard, egg) • Rice vinegar (rice vinegar, water, sugar, salt, potassium metabisulphite) (sulphites) • Chives • Zesty garlic blend (granulated garlic, cornmeal, salt, dehydrated red bell pepper flakes, spices, sugar, herbs, canola oil, silicon dioxide, citric acid) (sulphites).
